# Implementation Plan: Language Mode (Vietnamese to English)

This plan outlines the steps to introduce a language switching feature to the Adecos MVP, allowing users to toggle between Vietnamese (default) and English.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The default language will be set to Vietnamese ([vi](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/pages/LandingPage.jsx#59-64)). English (`en`) will be the alternative.
> The language switcher will be integrated into the Sidebar footer, near the theme toggle.

## Proposed Changes

### Infrastructure

#### [NEW] [i18n.js](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/i18n.js)
Setup the `i18next` configuration with `react-i18next` and `i18next-browser-languagedetector`.

#### [NEW] [vi/translation.json](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/locales/vi/translation.json)
Contains all strings currently in the application in Vietnamese.

#### [NEW] [en/translation.json](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/locales/en/translation.json)
Contains the English translations for all strings.

---

### Components

#### [MODIFY] [main.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/main.jsx)
Import `i18n.js` to initialize it at the root of the application.

#### [NEW] [LanguageSwitcher.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/components/LanguageSwitcher.jsx)
A sleek, minimal toggle or dropdown component to switch between languages.

#### [MODIFY] [Sidebar.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/components/Sidebar.jsx)
- Integrate `LanguageSwitcher` in the footer.
- Use `useTranslation` hook to translate navigation items.

---

### Content Migration

#### [MODIFY] [bentoGridData.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/data/bentoGridData.jsx)
Replace hardcoded Vietnamese strings with translation keys.

#### [MODIFY] [LandingPage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/pages/LandingPage.jsx)
Translate all hero sections, features, and CTA content using `useTranslation`.

#### [MODIFY] [WaitlistBanner.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/components/WaitlistBanner.jsx)
Translate the banner text and button.

#### [MODIFY] [ChatInput.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/components/chat/ChatInput.jsx)
Translate the placeholder text.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `npm run lint` to ensure no syntax errors.
- Create a new Playwright test `frontend/tests/language_switch.spec.js` to:
    1. Verify default language is Vietnamese (check for "AI Agent" as "AI Agent" or "Quản lý dự án").
    2. Toggle to English.
    3. Verify language changed (check for English text like "Project Management").

### Manual Verification
- Manually toggle between languages in the Sidebar.
- Refresh the page and ensure the selected language persists (via `i18next-browser-languagedetector`).
- Check all major pages (Landing, Chat, Projects) for consistent translation.
